{"tid":101493,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"求股票期權入門","createTime":"2017-01-31T00:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T17:34:12.000Z","uid":52315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2235df6e428410e991b74dfada2fe588b0f270","tid":101493,"uid":52315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T00:51:14.000Z","msg":"想問下有無入門文睇下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nthx"},{"pid":"0f5e3c94df48cce0a20020a6f16d24b807299b6b","tid":101493,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇，唔好試。<br />\n<br />\n申利: 夾死左"},{"pid":"82279f03f6c93d7f93f0f99d2e012fff60350db9","tid":101493,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:17:10.000Z","msg":"期權投機客"},{"pid":"f7b9023b563b0d4720d6af89abff91375dbc3af6","tid":101493,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"新手最好先玩多成交既期權  同埋唔好諗住個個月SP/SC 收錢  實會有一個月收皮"},{"pid":"04dc9c14c4b5a2b302737dc295e2bd544503d3b8","tid":101493,"uid":29608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:11:59.000Z","msg":"睇歐陽一心"},{"pid":"b046e3524f39a22dd8a7bd6c41693016b8aefc21","tid":101493,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:15:52.000Z","msg":"買8仔本書"},{"pid":"3241bd46e26c0a5f633061151ef50a40a75f612c","tid":101493,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下有無入門文睇下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nthx</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n11年到依家既上落市，剩做籃籌short call同put, 唔做太大gearing，收期權金賺時間值都收唔少"},{"pid":"127e45e262d273b42fd83bdc969414f992438890","tid":101493,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"呢幾年上落市係20000至24000點上落<br />\n所以預好個margin, 玩落去唔會損手得去邊<br />\n不過今年2017，風起雲湧，隨時出現單邊市夾死你，小心為上"},{"pid":"6b2ed9105059a1927d2029015014f88f63d5c6e0","tid":101493,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手最好先玩多成交既期權  同埋唔好諗住個個月SP/SC 收錢  實會有一個月收皮</blockquote><br />\n做Short可以控制勝升大過long<br />\n我自己多數assume 市場理性，引伸波幅同delta已經係最合理水平（當然前題下個期權係高流通量）<br />\n就算做short都有好多種玩法......價外定價內，到期日長定短，都需要自己做下走勢分析，計番個合理既buffer俾自己"},{"pid":"ebdbaec6c59654153904c8021c30ac3bc0f2d2ed","tid":101493,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手最好先玩多成交既期權  同埋唔好諗住個個月SP/SC 收錢  實會有一個月收皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沒錯"},{"pid":"cc8b1f5dab1203e366bfc7128b66f5e56c8341e0","tid":101493,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買8仔本書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nE本寫既野令你中伏"},{"pid":"5feeb4a605f4c13a80e6011fff91f2396bb0be87","tid":101493,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買8仔本書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nE本寫既野令你中伏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無咩經歷好深刻可以分亨下？<br />\n當係俾大家參考下"},{"pid":"de1b8fa1a92adfa09e75a614d4ae3e0514ebed32","tid":101493,"uid":52315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇歐陽一心</blockquote><br />\n睇緊一心哥本書 不過未明晒"},{"pid":"364a82b5825e6541973a68d4d556ee7a0430e4af","tid":101493,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:58:12.000Z","msg":"無人提John hull"},{"pid":"6255e1460322cd8c938f0cf1ae13266e3c23e19c","tid":101493,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>期權投機客</blockquote><br />\n依本野熱門到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://webcat.hkpl.gov.hk/lib/item?id=chamo:3348585&am